doc.FinishTransaction("layout");

Read the GoLayout User Guide for more details.

member.value:
A value of zero (the default) means there is no limit;
a positive value specifies a limit.
The default value is zero.

member.remarks:
Each  gets its properties from its parent node.
 is used for all default  property values;
 is ignored.

Each  gets its properties from its "grand-parent" node.
The root nodes get their defaults from ;
the immediate children of root nodes get their defaults from .

